OL,3,CFourth man charged in connection with
OL,4,Cdeath of Coventry teenager
OL,6,FA fourth man has been charged after
OL,7,Fthe death of a teenager in Coventry
OL,8,Fearlier this year.
OL,10,FIsmael Nabeel, 18, of Coventry, has
OL,11,Fbeen charged with murder and attempted
OL,12,Fmurder. Michael Ababio, 18 died after
OL,13,Fhe was stabbed near Foleshill Library,
OL,14,Fon 22 February.
OL,16,FThree others have previously been
OL,17,Fcharged with murder and attempted
OL,18,Fmurder.
