CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1778609470
OL,3,CFourth man charged in connection with
OL,4,Cdeath of Coventry teenager
OL,6,FMahad Mohammed, aged 19, was charged
OL,7,Fwith murder and attempted murder and
OL,8,Fhas been remanded in custody.
OL,10,FTwo 17-year-old boys, who cannot be
OL,11,Fnamed due to their age, were also
OL,12,Fcharged with murder and attempted
OL,13,Fmurder and appeared at Coventry
OL,14,FMagistrates' Court on 22 February,
OL,15,Fwhere they were also remanded in
OL,16,Fcustody.
OL,18,FNabeel has been remanded in custody
OL,19,Fand is due to appear at Coventry
OL,20,FMagistrates' Court, on Monday, May 11.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
