OL,3,CFourth man charged in connection with
OL,4,Cdeath of Coventry teenager
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Nigel Box, leading
OL,7,Fthe investigation, said: "Specially-
OL,8,Ftrained officers are continuing to
OL,9,Fsupport Michael's family and have
OL,10,Fupdated them on the latest
OL,11,Fdevelopments and charge in the case.
OL,13,F"Officers investigating have continued
OL,14,Fto work tirelessly to understand
OL,15,Fexactly what took place in February
OL,16,Fand lead to Michael's tragic death.
OL,18,F"We are continuing to appeal to anyone
OL,19,Fwho may not have spoken to us yet and
OL,20,Fhas any information that could help
OL,21,Four case to please make a report."
